abstract: List of four final candidates to become the chief prosecutor for the International Criminal Court is announced; Fatou Bensouda of Gamia is widely considered to be the front-runner.
snippet: A committee on Tuesday announced its list of four final candidates to become the chief prosecutor for the International Criminal Court.
lead_paragraph: A committee on Tuesday announced its list of four final candidates to become the chief prosecutor for the International Criminal Court.

headline.seo: Prosecutor Finalists Named for International Criminal Court
